servinfo.title: Precautions in Diagnosing Troubles (Vehicle Equipped with Auto Leveling Headlight System)

item.ptxt: Be sure to read Precautions for Electrical Circuit Service before inspection and observe what is written there.

Replacement of height sensor and headlight leveling control module.When height sensor and/or headlight leveling control module is replaced with new one, perform initialization of auto leveling headlight system according to Initialization of Auto Leveling Headlight System .
